This node specifies when the next notification should be presented to the user. 
Possible Values: 
"Off"; Descr=No automatic reminders;
"At Startup"; Descr=Reminder when the phone starts up; 
"1 Month"; Descr=Reminder one month from now;

(Read only) The UTC DateTime for the next notification if ReminderInterval is set to "One Month". When interval is "Off" or "At Startup", the value is 0. 
Possible Values: 
Integer; Descr=Number of seconds since midnight 1/1 1970 to the time for next reminder;
